<br>
Either you can die fighting, or die like a coward. <br>
<br>
You do seem to understand a little bit about the cycle, the Circle of Darkness that controls every soul in this world. You cannot fight against the Hate.<br>
<br>
If you do not fight, I'll start by taking your wife. Still wish not to fight? I'll take your children. Your friends, and all of your loved ones. Its not the first time, nor will it be the last.<br>
<br>
The Circle controled by the alliance of Innoruuk, Cazic Thule, and Rallos Zek will always remain unbroken. With Bertox bringing up the rear, all will fall and die sooner or later. <br>
<br>
I perfer you fight, but I have no qualms slaughtering a foolish elf not willing to fight back. I have done so before.<br>
<br>
Harden your heart if you think it will allow you to watch as I hang all you hold dear on wooden crosses, bound and gagged. <br>
<br>
I am a student of Primodial Malice, I know how to cause pain and suffering to beings. When you hear their screams and know the trueness of my darkness, will you be able to resist fighting?<br>
<br>
I think not. Even if you do, you would be next. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.leagueofshadows.net/"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> League Of Shadows</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
